984, \"to\": 1991}]}, {\"sentence\": \"As a human being, we have been blessed by Mother Nature with all the strength and it is upto us how we harness this great natural power towards a positive direction like nation building.\", \"from\": 2007, \"to\": 2193, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a human being\", \"from\": 2010, \"to\": 2023}, {\"ngram\": \"Mother Nature\", \"from\": 2049, \"to\": 2062}, {\"ngram\": \"all the strength\", \"from\": 2068, \"to\": 2084}, {\"ngram\": \"us\", \"from\": 2100, \"to\": 2102}, {\"ngram\": \"this great natural power\", \"from\": 2118, \"to\": 2142}, {\"ngram\": \"a positive direction\", \"from\": 2151, \"to\": 2171}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Under the visionary leadership of PM Modi ji, India is cruising ahead towards realising the vision of becoming an Atmanirbhar Bharat by 2047.\", \"from\": 2194, \"to\": 2335, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2240, \"end\": 2245, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/India\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 3.832406544634729e-20, \"text\": \"India\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/India\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/India\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the visionary leadership\", \"from\": 2200, \"to\": 2224}, {\"ngram\": \"PM\", \"from\": 2228, \"to\": 2230}, {\"ngram\": \"Modi ji\", \"from\": 2231, \"to\": 2238}, {\"ngram\": \"the vision\", \"from\": 2282, \"to\": 2292}, {\"ngram\": \"an Atmanirbhar Bharat\", \"from\": 2305, \"to\": 2326}]}, {\"sentence\": \"We must do whatever needs to be done to realise this vision.\", \"from\": 2336, \"to\": 2396, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"whatever\", \"from\": 2347, \"to\": 2355}, {\"ngram\": \"this vision\", \"from\": 2384, \"to\": 2395}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The tales of these wonderful women will inspire scores of women and youth to pursue something that they feel passionate about and are able to make a meaningful contribution.\", \"from\": 2397, \"to\": 2570, \"entities\